    <h1>Lemosho vs Machame: Which Kilimanjaro Route Is Right for You?</h1>
    <p>Head-to-head comparison of the Lemosho Route and Machame Route on Mount Kilimanjaro. Scenery, success rates, crowds, terrain, and the climber each route actually suits.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <span>By <a href="/about">Nelson Mushi</a></span>
      <span>&middot; 2026-06-14</span>
      <span>&middot; <a href="/blog">Back to Blog</a></span>
    </div>
  </div>
